OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FProceedings were initially issued
OL,8,Fafter councillors in Belfast approved
OL,9,Fa draft Irish language policy in
OL,10,FOctober last year.
OL,12,FThe blueprint aims to promote the use
OL,13,Fof Irish in public life, with
OL,14,Fbilingual signage and logos to appear
OL,15,Fon council facilities, signage and
OL,16,Funiforms.
OL,18,FAmid unionist objections, a call-in
OL,19,Fmechanism was triggered to scrutinise
OL,20,Fthe legitimacy of the decision.
