OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FUnder the procedure a 15% minority of
OL,8,Fcouncillors can request a
OL,9,Freconsideration which involves seeking
OL,10,Flegal opinion on any potential adverse
OL,11,Fcommunity impact.
OL,13,FIf those concerns are assessed as
OL,14,Fbeing valid, an 80% super majority may
OL,15,Fbe required in a call-in for the
OL,16,Foriginal motion to be voted in again.
OL,18,FThe draft Irish language policy for
OL,19,FBelfast currently remains on hold
OL,20,Fpending the outcome of that process
OL,21,Fsometime early next year.
