OL,7,FMs McClure is pressing ahead with her
OL,8,Fcase based on claims the Council has
OL,9,Fwrongly interpreted relevant sections
OL,10,Fof the Local Government (Northern
OL,11,FIreland) Act 2014.
OL,13,FThe action widened out into a systemic
OL,14,Fchallenge after the authority backed a
OL,15,FSinn Fein proposal to fly the
OL,16,FPalestinian flag for one day at City
OL,17,FHall.
OL,19,FUnionists again objected and called in
OL,20,Fthe original decision taken to mark
OL,21,FPalestinian Solidarity Day.
