OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FBut following a further vote the flag
OL,8,Fwas raised shortly after midnight on
OL,9,FMonday.
OL,11,FThe following day a High Court judge
OL,12,Frefused an emergency legal bid by Ms
OL,13,FMcClure to have it taken down.
OL,15,FIn the wider challenge, her lawyers
OL,16,Fcontend that the council has
OL,17,Funlawfully created a new "filter
OL,18,Fprocess" in call-ins which allows
OL,19,Fcontroversial motions to be passed by
OL,20,Fa simple majority.
