OL,7,FThe minority safeguard has been
OL,8,Fnullified in key votes where a
OL,9,Fqualified majority should be required
OL,10,Firrespective of legal opinion, they
OL,11,Fcontend.
OL,13,FIn court today, the council's
OL,14,Fbarrister questioned Ms McClure's
OL,15,Fright to take legal action over its
OL,16,Finternal procedures.
OL,18,FDenise Kiley KC said: "There is a
OL,19,Fjurisdictional issue the council takes
OL,20,Fin terms of standing."
