OL,13,Falleged in connection with the
OL,14,FPalestinian flag row.
OL,16,F"The applicant's affidavit evidence
OL,17,Fonly touches on her standing in
OL,18,Frespect of the Irish language strategy
OL,19,Fcall-in," Ms Kiley submitted.
