OL,7,FAt one stage Ms McClure's barrister,
OL,8,FJohn Larkin KC, sought an undertaking
OL,9,Ffrom the Council not to take any
OL,10,Ffurther decision before the judicial
OL,11,Freview is determined.
OL,13,F"We really don't want to have to
OL,14,Ftrouble the court with any application
OL,15,Ffor interim relief," he said.
OL,17,FInstead, Ms Kiley stressed that it
OL,18,Fremains unknown when the issues will
OL,19,Fbe tabled again for reconsideration.
